atoms.name: Obsidian_Shard
atoms.description: A jagged, black shard of obsidian with razor-sharp edges, capable of cutting through flesh and bone with ease. It hums with a faint, eerie energy when exposed to moonlight.

atoms.name: Whispering_Wind
atoms.description: A gust of wind that carries the whispers of the forgotten, carrying secrets and curses from the depths of the forest. It can be harnessed to guide or mislead travelers.

atoms.name: Glowcap_Mushroom
atoms.description: A bioluminescent mushroom that emits a soft, eerie glow. When consumed, it grants temporary night vision and enhances the user's ability to sense nearby creatures.

atoms.name: Bone_Harvester
atoms.description: A skeletal creature that burrows underground, leaving behind a trail of bones. It can be tamed to harvest resources or used as a living tool for digging.

atoms.name: Shadow_Clinger
atoms.description: A sentient patch of darkness that clings to surfaces and creatures alike. It can absorb light, providing stealth in dark environments, but it also drains the vitality of those it touches.

atoms.name: Elder_Tree_Sap
atoms.description: A thick, viscous sap from an ancient tree, imbued with the wisdom and power of the forest. It can be used to heal wounds or create powerful potions.

molecules.name: Dagger_of_Whispers
molecules.description: A dagger forged from obsidian shards, its blade inscribed with ancient runes that whisper secrets when drawn. Requires a sharp material and something that carries whispers.

molecules.name: Stealth_Cloak
molecules.description: A cloak woven from shadow clingers and glowcap mushrooms, granting the wearer the ability to blend into darkness while enhancing their night vision. Requires a material that provides stealth in dark environments and something that enhances night vision.

molecules.name: Wisdom_Potion
molecules.description: A potent potion brewed from elder tree sap, granting the drinker temporary wisdom and enhanced perception. It can also be used to heal wounds. Requires a material imbued with wisdom and something that can heal wounds.
